{
  "stem": "23737.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mind you, we didn't get any soup on the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the middle.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the middle.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had no guards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No guards at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I haven't seen any guards in all of the time I was in the camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I haven't seen any guards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, absolutely nothing-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, only when we got to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we arrived in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were-- in Theresienstadt there were soldier barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How do you call these buildings-- where the soldiers live always.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in these buildings were refugees already who were brought there from other places earlier.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we arrived, we were taken to one of the squares that was surrounded by these barracks, because they had no idea where to put us at that moment.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as we were sitting there on the ground on our luggage, tired, and hungry, and everything, my friend who was the boss in our block, he went around the windows and started talking to people that-- where are you from?",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What city?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What village?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you won't believe it, but he found his mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was inside the building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From their village, she was brought to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was inside the building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had a little more information about what was going on in the world.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And through these people, we heard that some part of Germany has already been liberated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the war is to end very shortly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then after that, I got typhoid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was very ill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I, I don't know what happened in the next couple of weeks until the liberation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were liberated on the 6th of May end of the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know-- possibly on the road [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in me already.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
